des: Each day the Dwell Kansas City Residential Real Estate team lead and podcast host, Jay Swearingen, introduces our listeners to another great reason to enjoy Kansas City. From festivals to cultural amenities to dive bars, Jay focuses our attention on things you can do this week to get out and enjoy Kansas City.
